paragraphs.text: helllo my dear friends! well, here i am on record at last. and it feels so wonderful to be here with you on my first album
i'm so happy! aha! happy go lucky me! i just go my way, living everyday! i don't worry! worrying don't agree, things that bother you, never bother me!
things that bother you, never bother me i feel happy and fine! aha! living in the sunlight, loving in the moonlight having a wonderful time!
haven't got a lot, i don't need a lot coffee's only a dime living in the sunlight, loving in the moonlight, having a wonderful time!
just take it from me, i'm just as free as any daughter. i do what i like, just what i like, and how i love it!
i'm right here to stay when i'm old and gray, i'll be right in my prime! living in the sunlight, loving in the moonlight, having a wonderful time!
